{
  "stem": "1873.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I did go to his assistant, I took 20 zlotys which I had from the cigarettes, did give him the 20 zlotys and told him, look, I am sick really.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he motioned-- he motioned me to the people who were already selected to be taken out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In this way, I find myself in a group of 20 people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And-- and later the gates open, they took us out into street to the streets of Stryj.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was cold, it was winter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'4-- I don't-- Now, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was it at the end of-- oh, maybe this will give me an idea.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A short time before, one of the prisoners did get a package with food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in a-- in the newspaper, it talked about [INAUDIBLE] surrending-- surrounding-- surrending-- surrrending--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- in-- in Russia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So if I could find a date, I would know exactly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was maybe a week later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were so happy that the German armies defeated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I still remember what kind of feeling we had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, we in the streets.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I decided to run.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had come to some [INAUDIBLE] streets, I will run.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were guarded, but not by Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were guarded by Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the Jewish police considered us sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So no one actual-- in the front, they were flirting with some girls.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were lead to the-- and I thought I will jump to a side street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But now, near me-- close to me was a man maybe 20 some years old.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he did look healthy to me, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I thought maybe he want to escape, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we start to talk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, yes, but not now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father's in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We go to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
